{"tid":1153851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半山般咸道女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-14T01:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T02:00:59.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f9737f7f820b18506eda5768ab4b91d2eaadb9","tid":1153851,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DQg7nsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDQg7nsD.png&h=5266f604&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p78p87E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp78p87E.png&h=044855a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西營盤般咸道19號，凌晨零時許，一名41歲姓鄭女子，從大廈高處墮下，一聲巨響後，倒卧在簷篷上昏迷不醒，保安發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防員趕至現場協助，但救護員證實女子已當場死亡。警員聯絡死者家人協助調查，現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步無可疑。據知她有精神病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=32556fbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"53b299417df1a59951e93966a828893c3ca491f8","tid":1153851,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"公屋-1"},{"pid":"52a60a41cdfe4e1519ea7757ac4573029b3394e7","tid":1153851,"uid":248636,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"53b299417df1a59951e93966a828893c3ca491f8","tid":1153851,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:55:27.000Z","msg":"公屋-1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:56:03.000Z","msg":"關公屋咩事？"},{"pid":"4f97ff1baa806c75082efc0480038c158f36c07b","tid":1153851,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"創造精神病is 魔鬼定上帝?"},{"pid":"4